NBA Top 10: Revija zakucavanja [VIDEO]
05 Nov 2019, 12:55 by Nemanja
Zakucavanje centra Filadelfija Seventisiksersa Al Horforda u duelu sa Finiks Sansima proglašeno je za najbolji potez protekle večeri u NBA ligi.
,,Dank šou“ u NBA ligi protekle večeri, gde su mesta na listi najboljih poteza uglavnom zauzimala zakucavanja širom američkog tla.
Pored Horforda, na listi su se našli Janis Adetokumbo, Devin Buker i mnogi drugi…

NBA Top 10: Stunt Show [VIDEO]
05 Nov 2019, 12:55 by Nemanja
The locking down of Philadelphia Seventisiksers center Al Horford in a duel with the Phoenix Sansims was declared the best move last night in the NBA.
The NBA's "Dunk Show" last night, where places on the top roster have mostly taken a dive all over American soil.
In addition to Horford, Janis Adetokumbo, Devin Booker and many others were on the list…
